        "description": {
            "value": "<p>With soothing song or tales, you lull the target into an enchanting dream. When you cast the spell, the target falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} if it wasn't already. While Unconscious, it experiences a dream of your choice.</p>\n<p>If it sleeps for at least 1 minute, it gains the benefit of the dream for the remainder of the spell's duration.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Sweet Dream (Insight)]{Dream of Insight}</strong> +1 status bonus to Intelligence-based skill checks</li>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Sweet Dream (Glamour)]{Dream of Glamour}</strong> +1 status bonus to Charisma-based skill checks</li>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Sweet Dream (Voyaging)]{Dream of Voyaging}</strong> +5-foot status bonus to Speed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you Cast this Spell again, the effects of any previous sweet dream you cast end.</p>"
